How well can your sys admin defend against a hack? 
How well do your locks fare against a ramset? 
Are you using Mifare classics for your access cards?
Are all your servers patched? 
How frequently is your AV DB being refreshed?

Its better to be patched than hacked. 

You have great security, but do you have a red team? #redteam

InfoSec is NOT an investment, its a cost of doing business.  

Red teaming is simulation of a potential attack on your organization, wherein everything that can go wrong, will go wrong. A red team audit is crucial in securing your organization. 
